(1358, '<p>Make your birthday party an unforgettable experience at Virtual Realms!</p>\n<p>Whether you’re celebrating a milestone or just want to have a blast with friends and family, we offer birthday packages for groups of all ages.</p>'),
(1359, '<p>Your child&rsquo;s Bar/Bat Mitzvah is a once-in-a-lifetime event. That&rsquo;s why it&rsquo;s important to cherish and celebrate the day.</p>'),
(1362, '<p>From family reunions and graduations to holiday office parties and corporate events, we can help you liven up any special occasion!</p>\n<p>With cutting-edge equipment and a vast library of incredible VR games...</p>'),
(1360, '<p>Improve workplace collaboration with the aid of fun and challenging VR experiences!</p>\n<p>Leverage our growing collection of teamwork-centric games to supercharge your teams\' efficiency and cohesion.</p>'),
(1361, '<p>From family reunions and graduations to holiday office parties and corporate events, we can help you liven up any special occasion!</p>\n<p>With cutting-edge equipment and a vast library of incredible VR games...</p>');
